data.description:
Explore comfort and style in this modern four-bedroom home, just three years NEW in a gated community. 
The heart of the home boasts an oversized kitchen island and a spacious walk-in pantry for practical yet stylish living. 
Enjoy the balcony off the primary bedroom and the convenience of dual walk-in closets. 
With low HOA, a low-maintenance yard featuring a covered patio, and proximity to shopping and restaurants, this residence offers a perfect blend of convenience and contemporary living. Your ideal home awaits!
